subject: Football

Football (College)
lead_paragraph: Winston Fraser returned an interception 71 yards and T. Y. Hilton scored touchdowns on his first two catches as Florida International University upset host Louisville, 24-17, for the Panthers’ first win in six tries against teams from the Big East Conference.
